export const getNewPersons = newPersons => fetch(`https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/?page=${newPersons}`).then(initial => initial.json().then(json => initial.ok ? Promise.resolve(json) : Promise.reject(json)));
export const getNamePersons = namePersons => fetch(`https://rickandmortyapi.com/api/character/?page=${namePersons}`).then(initial => initial.json().then(json => initial.ok ? Promise.resolve(json) : Promise.reject(json)));
